<article class="post--single post-687 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-dairy-free category-fall category-gluten-free category-perennial-favorite category-spring category-summer category-vegan category-vegetable category-vegetarian category-winter tag-everyday-cooking tag-france tag-memory tag-paris ingredients-carrots ingredients-garlic ingredients-onion ingredients-thyme" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">
